# ==========================================================
# Cohesity Backup Validation – DISPLAY + TXT + CSV OUTPUT
# GET ONLY | SEARCH ONLY | FAST CLUSTER DISCOVERY
#
# Output:
# InputCI | BackupType | ObjectName | ClusterName | ProtectionGroup | LastBackupTime
#
# Desired example:
# PAYROLLDB@SERVER01 | Oracle | PAYROLLDB | ClusterA | PG_ORA_PAYROLL | 22-Jun-2026 01:10:00 ET
# PAYROLLDB@SERVER01 | FS     | SERVER01  | ClusterA | PG_SERVER01_OS | 22-Jun-2026 00:30:00 ET
#
# Key Logic:
# - DBNAME@SERVERNAME is treated as a targeted check.
# - For DBNAME@SERVERNAME:
#     * SQL/Oracle rows must match DBNAME only.
#     * FS rows must match SERVERNAME only.
#     * Other DBs on the same server are not printed.
# - For SERVERNAME only:
#     * Script can show multiple DBs found for that server.
#     * Script can show FS/server backup.
# - BackupType is derived from Cohesity environment/type metadata only.
# - ObjectName primarily comes from protected-object .name.
# - SQL/Oracle prefer kRegular/Regular and ignore kLog/Log.
# - Source/original row is preferred over replicated row.
# - Validation CSV is not generated. Placeholder only is kept commented.
# ==========================================================

$ErrorActionPreference = "Stop"
$FormatEnumerationLimit = -1
